Our Technology

Our Commitment to Stray Dogs

At StrayTrack, we believe in a future where every stray dog is cared for and loved. Founded in 2023, our journey began with a passion for animal welfare and a vision to tackle the challenges faced by stray dogs. Our mission is to enhance their quality of life through innovative tracking solutions, utilizing advanced technologies like QR codes and RFID tags. We are dedicated to collaborating with communities and animal welfare organizations to promote responsible pet ownership and ensure the safety and health of stray dogs. Our core values include compassion for all animals, innovation in animal welfare, and a commitment to education and awareness. Together, we can make a difference in the lives of these vulnerable animals.

Discover Our Innovative Tracking Technology

At StrayTrack, we utilize cutting-edge QR codes and RFID tags to efficiently monitor stray dogs. This technology provides instant access to vital information, ensuring the safety and well-being of these animals while supporting responsible pet ownership.

Explore Our Innovative Features

StrayTrack offers a comprehensive solution for managing stray dogs through advanced technology. Our platform provides easy access to health records and vaccination history, ensuring the well-being of stray dogs. By utilizing QR codes and RFID tags, we empower animal welfare organizations and local authorities to efficiently monitor and manage stray dogs, promoting responsible pet ownership and community safety.
Stray Dog Tracking System
Our system uses QR codes and RFID tags to monitor stray dogs in real-time. This ensures quick access to their health records and vaccination history, promoting their safety and well-being.
